requests, Exp API will have to fetch the required UserID from either x-user=
id request header or from x-access-token request header and then pass the r=
equired userid accordingly
 =20
 =20
if(request.searchBy =3D=3D=3D "approverUserId")
{
   var approverUserId=3D apiHeaders['x-userId'] //or read userId from apiHe=
aders['x-access-token']
   // Map the above approverUserId to DSR request.approverUserId when calli=
ng DSR CAP API to search for checker workflow requests
}</pre>
