<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><u><strong>Checker:</strong></u> As p=
er the Checker request, the API will return the list of workflow requests a=
waiting approval from the logged in Checker.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><u><strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(=
23,43,77);">Exp API Response processing</span></span></strong></u></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"=
>The Exp API will loop through the service Request list and deserialise the=
 API Json string to the respective object</span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
