"Authorise", "Reject"&nbsp; "Cancel"</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">&nbsp;</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper"><br>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(163,21,21);">If th=
e viewType is for a Checker(viewType=3D=3D=3DChecker) and the workflow is s=
till awaiting checker(logged in user) approval, then display</span></p><p s=
tyle=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(163,21,21);">"Authoris=
e", "Reject" &amp; "Cancel" action buttons on the UI</span></p><p style=3D"=
text-align: left;"><br></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(163,21,21);">If the viewType is for a maker(viewType=3D=3D=3DMaker=
), then display</span></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"col=
or: rgb(163,21,21);">"Cancel" action button on the UI</span></p><p style=3D=
"text-align: left;"><br></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"c=
olor: rgb(163,21,21);">Refer to the "Processing Condition/Logic" column for=
 mapping details/logic</span></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p></t=
d>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">// For ma=
ker, display the "Cancel" button alone as per the below logic,
if viewType =3D=3D=3D Maker then
Display "Cancel" button on the UI

// For Checker, display the last mile action buttons as per the below logic=
,
if viewType =3D=3D=3D Checker &amp;&amp; (entities.approvalWorkflowDetails[=
0].workflowStatus =3D=3D=3D "ApprovalPending" &amp;&amp; entities.approvalW=
orkflowDetails[0].approvalData.approvers.filter(approver =3D&gt; approver.u=
serId =3D=3D=3D logged in userId &amp;&amp; approver.userIdScheme =3D=3D=3D=
  "CustomerInternalId" &amp;&amp; approver.status =3D=3D=3D "ApprovalPendin=
g").length &gt; 0)) then
{
 &nbsp; &nbsp;Display "Authorise", "Reject" and "Cancel" button on the UI
}
else
{
 &nbsp; &nbsp;Display "Cancel" button on the UI
}
=09</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
</tr>
